# Created: 2025-08-05
# Purpose: To prevent committing secrets and unnecessary files to version control,
# supporting SOC 2 principles of Security and Confidentiality.

# Dependencies
# Ignore all node_modules directories in the project.
node_modules/

# Environment variables
# Ignore .env files in the root directory and ALL subdirectories.
# The ** glob pattern is crucial for finding files in sub-folders like /server/
**/.env

# Logs
# Prevent staging of log files, which can contain sensitive data.
logs
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Other common ignores for Node projects
.DS_Store